24/11/2010
BELGRADE, Serbia -- Turbofolk diva Svetlana Ceca Raznatovic is facing embezzlement charges, local media reported on Tuesday (November 23rd). Prosecutors are working on an indictment expected to charge her with misappropriating 2.2m euros in trading football players from the Obilic club she headed to foreign clubs. Raznatovic also faces charges of illegal possession of fire arms found at her home in 2003. (B92, RTS, Blic, Tanjug, AP - 23/11/10)
